\id EPH - Kaluli Bible 
\h Aęž‰fesaęž‰s 
\toc1 Moęž‰foęž‰s We Foęž‰l Eyoęž‰ Aęž‰fesaęž‰s Kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰ Saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰ 
\toc2 Aęž‰fesaęž‰s 
\toc3 Aęž‰fe 
\mt2 Moęž‰foęž‰s We Foęž‰l Eyoęž‰  
\mt1 Aęž‰fesaęž‰s  
\mt2 Kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰ Saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰  
\imt1 Asulumaęž‰noęž‰ Towoęž‰ We  
\ip Foęž‰l eloęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ wenamioęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ wengoęž‰ iliki saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Gode eyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kelegoęž‰ daęž‰lab we tambo aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Hebeneloęž‰ kelegoęž‰ daęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ kegeneliaęž‰gaęž‰ diaęž‰taki, Yaęž‰su Keliso e haęž‰ga tambo difaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Keliso e kelegoęž‰ tambo daęž‰lab wemaęž‰ misaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab. (1.10) Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ tambo Kelisowa mada kudaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki, e oęž‰liaęž‰ koęž‰ngoęž‰ meseaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰. Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s heb wenamioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene kanuloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Kelisowa tilidaęž‰dalikiyoęž‰, i aęž‰noęž‰ tambo gaęž‰li meseaęž‰ki sili alitaki, soęž‰loęž‰ imilise faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib. Keliso eloęž‰ nanog dimidoęž‰ aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ ene gasili. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale enoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki daęž‰fe alifaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tambo, ene Mama Maliloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ imoęž‰ dimi. Mama e kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰liaęž‰ iliki, nafa kelegoęž‰ enedoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ka dimidaęž‰melaęž‰ib. (1.14) Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to heb andeb aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, Keliso kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwa kudoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, iyoęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ imilise dowaki, Godeyaęž‰ ene man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi.  
\ip Kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ Kelisowa kudab aęž‰namioęž‰, iyoęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰ imilise dowab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ imilise faęž‰laęž‰dowab koęž‰loęž‰, doęž‰moęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ misaęž‰yoęž‰ Yaęž‰su. (4.1-16) Godeyaęž‰ ene kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ a imilise oęž‰ngoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowab koęž‰loęž‰, Keliso e ili a kuan amiloęž‰ aikoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dowab. (2.19-22) Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Gode amiloęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ tambo ga oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, ili inoęž‰ Keliso koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab. (5.22-32)  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1.1 \xt Ilig 18.19-21, 19.1\x*Ne Foęž‰l, ne Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰ asulab aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ enedoęž‰ iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu nowoęž‰ ne koęž‰loęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰. Niyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we Aęž‰fesaęž‰s amisaęž‰n aęž‰namiloęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene kalukaęž‰isale, Yaęž‰su Keliso hendeleloęž‰ kudu haęž‰nab imoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l.  
\v 2 Do Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, haęž‰saloęž‰ mesaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, gi oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰ki dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.   
\s1 Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ nanog dimidoęž‰ amioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ nafaleyoęž‰ nimoęž‰ dimi  
\p
\v 3 \x - \xo 1.3 \xt Aęž‰fe 2.6\x*Nili mama asuwaęž‰takiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰ kudu alitaki, Hebeneloęž‰ nafa kelegoęž‰ daęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ tambo nimoęž‰woęž‰ dimi. Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niliyoęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ iya Godeyaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ wabulu saęž‰laęž‰melaęž‰niki.  
\v 4-5 \x - \xo 1.4-5 \xt Yoęž‰n 15.16\x*\x - \xo 1.4-5 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.12\x*Taminde amioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ we oęž‰semoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ amioęž‰, nioęž‰ Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰ domaęž‰ki, Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ aęž‰na daęž‰fe alifaęž‰. Eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ mogagoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dimidaki, maliloęž‰ nafale domaęž‰ki goęž‰. Hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ mada alan asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ nanog dimidamaęž‰ib aęž‰namioęž‰, nioęž‰ ene soęž‰wale domaęž‰ki aęž‰laęž‰liki daęž‰fe alifaęž‰. Enedoęž‰ asulab au daęž‰feyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ e mada sagaloęž‰.  
\v 6 Gode eyoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ mada alan disaęž‰lakiyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, niliyoęž‰ Gode aęž‰noęž‰ wabulumaęž‰niki. Eyoęž‰ ene soęž‰wayoęž‰ alan asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, eya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lakiyoęž‰, egoęž‰le dofoęž‰meleaęž‰kigab.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1.7 \xt Aęž‰fe 2.7, Kolo 1.14\x*Nioęž‰ sili alifomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ene soęž‰wayaęž‰ hoęž‰boęž‰ tuloęž‰ aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰ nioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ kililiaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, nili mogagoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na halaęž‰. Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, ene haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ mada alan aęž‰laęž‰widakigab.  
\v 8 Gode eyoęž‰ ene haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ modoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dimi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ asuloęž‰ nafa oęž‰liaęž‰ dinafaloęž‰ mesaęž‰noęž‰ asulan oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ nimoęž‰ dimi.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1.9 \xt Lom 16.25\x*Tamin amioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ nafa dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ dimidali aęž‰noęž‰ woęž‰noęž‰le diaęž‰foęž‰len koęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰ kalaba widoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ e sagale alitakigab.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1.10 \xt Kolo 1.16,20\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ eloęž‰ dimadali koęž‰loęž‰ delenoęž‰ we. Hoęž‰lende aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, Hebene kelegoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kelegoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ halaidoęž‰ haęž‰ga tambo kegene domaęž‰ki taęž‰faęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 1.11 \xt Lom 8.28-29\x*Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰ kudalikiyoęž‰, ene soęž‰walemoęž‰loęž‰ dabun dimiaęž‰ib aęž‰noęž‰ nimoęž‰ dimaęž‰ki daęž‰fe alifaęž‰. Gode eyoęž‰ taminde amioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidaliaęž‰gaęž‰ difaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kelegoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tambo Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰kiloęž‰ asulab au kudu haęž‰naki faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰sen.  
\v 12 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isale nioęž‰, Keliso amioęž‰ ni koęž‰le tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, niliyoęž‰ ene wi alan aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ wabulumaęž‰niki goęž‰.  
\v 13 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yu kalukaęž‰isalema gioęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasili to hendele aęž‰noęž‰ dabu koęž‰loęž‰, to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, gioęž‰ Yaęž‰suwa tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰namioęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ enedoęž‰ dinali sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, ene Mama Maliloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gimoęž‰ dimi. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, gioęž‰ enoęž‰lekaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki widaki goęž‰.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1.14 \xt 2Kol 1.22\x*Godeyaęž‰ ene Mama koęž‰loęž‰ ni amioęž‰ dowab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ kelegoęž‰ nafale koęž‰loęž‰ ene soęž‰walemoęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰ib aęž‰noęž‰ nioęž‰ hendele diaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰widakigab. Hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ gasiliaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ sili alifaęž‰ib, moęž‰woęž‰ nioęž‰ Gode enoęž‰le koęž‰loęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ wi alan aęž‰noęž‰ wabulu saęž‰laęž‰melaęž‰niki.   
\s1 Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Aęž‰fesaęž‰s kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ asuloęž‰ nafayoęž‰ dimaęž‰ki, Godemoęž‰ dulugu sioęž‰  
\p
\v 15-16 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gililoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Alan amiloęž‰ halale tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, Keliso kalukaęž‰isale nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰sen man aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ ne dabu koęž‰loęž‰, niyoęž‰ ge asulakiyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰sen. Mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰likiloęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰edaki, gioęž‰ asulufoęž‰likiyoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 1.17 \xt Kolo 1.9\x*Niyoęž‰ nili Do Gode Halaidoęž‰, Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene Gode oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰loęž‰l. Gode enenoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ fanda widaki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ asuloęž‰ nafayoęž‰ diminaęž‰ki, niyoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l. Aęž‰laęž‰galikiyoęž‰ gioęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ mada fanda asulumaęž‰ib.  
\v 18 Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰namiloęž‰ dimidamaęž‰ib aęž‰noęž‰ hendele faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰, gioęž‰ fanda baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ asulumaęž‰ki, niyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l. Kelegoęž‰ nafale koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene soęž‰walemoęž‰loęž‰ enedoęž‰ dimiaęž‰nigab aęž‰noęž‰ gioęž‰ asulufoęž‰meleaęž‰ki, dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.   
\p
\v 19-20 \x - \xo 1.19-20 \xt Kolo 1.11\x*\x - \xo 1.19-20 \xt Song 110.1, 2Kol 13.4, Kolo 2.12\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰ alan aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ asulumaęž‰ki, Godemoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l. Niliyoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰fe baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰ililoęž‰. Ene halaidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale nioęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Keliso e sowabiki, Godeyaęž‰ halaidoęž‰ alan aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ e aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰dasi alitaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, e Hebene halonamioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene dagi ililiba meseaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 1.21 \xt Kolo 1.16, 2.10\x*Keliso e Hebene halona silikiyoęž‰, maęž‰mulaęž‰ kalu oęž‰liaęž‰, mama koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ halaidoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ wiloęž‰ di aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, tambo Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ haęž‰ga taęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ taęž‰i haęž‰nab wenamioęž‰loęž‰ tif amioęž‰loęž‰ taęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰loęž‰, E misaęž‰ siliki tambo boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰ib.  
\v 22-23 \x - \xo 1.22-23 \xt Song 8.6\x*\x - \xo 1.22-23 \xt Lom 12.5, Aęž‰fe 4.10,15, Kolo 1.18\x*Gode eyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰woęž‰ tambo diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Kelisowaęž‰ halaidoęž‰ haęž‰ga dofoęž‰meleaęž‰ki taęž‰takiyoęž‰, e kelegoęž‰ tambo amioęž‰ misaęž‰ dofoęž‰meleaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ enedoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki goęž‰. Kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰ saęž‰s enedoęž‰woęž‰ i oęž‰m koęž‰loęž‰, iyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰le dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Eyoęž‰ saęž‰s amioęž‰ ene melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ waęž‰li alitaęž‰gaęž‰, kelegoęž‰ tambowoęž‰ ilili alifaęž‰.   
\c 2  
\s1 Gode eyoęž‰ sowoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale nioęž‰ Yaęž‰su oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dasi alitaki melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dimi  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 2.1 \xt Kolo 1.21, 2.13\x*Tamin amioęž‰ gililoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰len aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, gili mamayoęž‰ sofoęž‰len.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 2.2 \xt Kolo 3.7, Tait 3.3\x*Hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, gioęž‰ henfeloęž‰ mande we koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰likiyoęž‰, henfeloęž‰ weloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan mama mogagoęž‰woęž‰, Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ e koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰len. Kalukaęž‰isale Godeloęž‰ gola baęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰ Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ e iya iliki, nanogoęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2.3 \xt Kolo 3.6\x*Nioęž‰loęž‰ tamin amioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ sen koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ nili asuloęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ mogagoęž‰ asulan aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ asulab au dimidaęž‰len. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale nol koęž‰loęž‰ elen oęž‰leaumboęž‰, nioęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ gadioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰ga elen.  
