\v 14 \x - \xo 2.14 \xt 1Kol 12.13\x*Yaęž‰su Keliso e niloęž‰ haęž‰sa meseaęž‰kiloęž‰ dimidan kaluwoęž‰ e koęž‰loęž‰, Yu kalu oęž‰liaęž‰ Yu kaluma i oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gis dofoęž‰liki, gulusen aęž‰noęž‰ e goęž‰goęž‰daki tofaęž‰. Gis elen aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ ilif geloęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ iliki gulusen koęž‰sega, Yaęž‰su e sowoęž‰ aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, ilif aęž‰noęž‰ hugulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ imilig taęž‰foęž‰.  
