\v 12 \x - \xo 3.12 \xt Yoęž‰n 14.6, Lom 5.2\x*Nioęž‰ Yaęž‰suwa tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ kudalikiyoęž‰, eya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ moęž‰tagilaki, Godeloęž‰ amioęž‰ sagalaęž‰liki oęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 13 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gi asuwaęž‰takiloęž‰ niloęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ dioęž‰l we giliyoęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, gioęž‰ tagilakiyoęž‰ tilidabuwoęž‰ taiyabenaęž‰ki halale dowaęž‰bi. Moęž‰woęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ niloęž‰ dioęž‰l aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ halaidoęž‰ nafale mesaęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰fomaęž‰ki goęž‰.   
\s1 Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ Aęž‰fesaęž‰s kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ halale alifomaęž‰ki dulugu sioęž‰  
\p
\v 14 Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ nafale dimidaefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, ne Do Godeyaęž‰ haęž‰ga gulalu siliki e koęž‰loęž‰ wabudaęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 15 Hebeneloęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ sab oęž‰liaęž‰, henfeloęž‰ wiloęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ sab i oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰, moęž‰woęž‰ Gode e koęž‰loęž‰, eyoęž‰ inin wi hendeleyoęž‰ wikili alifaęž‰.  
\v 16 Gode eyamioęž‰ kelegoęž‰woęž‰ mada nafale modoęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene Mamayoęž‰ gili asuloęž‰ usamioęž‰ ililitaki, Godeyaęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ halale alifomaęž‰ki dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3.17 \xt Yoęž‰n 14.23, Kolo 1.23, 2.7\x*Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰ gililoęž‰ tilidabu aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, Keliso e gili asuloęž‰ usa dofoęž‰meleaęž‰ki dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l. I tef koęž‰loęž‰ hena tefele haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ halale kagayan aumboęž‰, gioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ alan asulan man us aęž‰na tinaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ halaidoęž‰le kagafoęž‰melaęž‰ib.  
\v 18-19 Aęž‰na halale kagayalikiyoęž‰, gi oęž‰liaęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ tambo halaidoęž‰woęž‰ diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ alan asulan manoęž‰ weoęž‰ngoęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ gioęž‰ dinafa fanda asulumaęž‰ki dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l. Yaęž‰suwaęž‰loęž‰ alan asulan man aęž‰noęž‰ ololoboęž‰loęž‰, aloloboęž‰loęž‰, osoloboęž‰loęž‰, andoloboęž‰loęž‰ aneyoęž‰, moęž‰elemaęž‰noęž‰ dowaki, kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰fanda asululiaęž‰noęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰sega gioęž‰ asulumaęž‰kiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l. Giliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene man nafa aęž‰noęž‰ gi amioęž‰ ililitaki waęž‰lifaęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 20 Godeyaęž‰ ene halaidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ni usamioęž‰ nanogoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dialikiyoęž‰, halaidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nililoęž‰ dabu baęž‰daboęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nili asuloęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ tininitaęž‰gaęž‰, mada alan noloęž‰ aęž‰dimidaęž‰sen.  
\v 21 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niliyoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ wabulumaęž‰niki. Kalukaęž‰isale Yaęž‰su Kelisowa kudakiloęž‰ ene saęž‰s dowab i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tamboloęž‰ taęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, dulugu saęž‰laęž‰melaęž‰niki. Hendele.   
\c 4  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 4.1 \xt Kolo 1.10\x*Ne Kalu Alanaęž‰ wiya iliki dibolo aya soęž‰l koęž‰loęž‰, niyoęž‰ towoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰soęž‰loęž‰l. Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ enoęž‰le domaęž‰ki hoęž‰leliaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab oęž‰leau, man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 4.2 \xt Kolo 3.12-13\x*Gode eyoęž‰ man gililoęž‰ kudu hamanaęž‰kiloęž‰ asulaboęž‰ we. Tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale no oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰, goęž‰noęž‰n ge haęž‰ga dowan, no oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰sa dowan, boęž‰eboęž‰ moęž‰iligan, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu abeyoęž‰ moęž‰ililoęž‰ dimidalega giliyoęž‰ emoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰moęž‰beaki, haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰bi.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 4.3 \xt Kolo 3.14-15\x*Godeyaęž‰ Mama eyoęž‰ haęž‰sa dowan man aęž‰maęž‰ ilikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ uwa kegene alifaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo uwaloęž‰ kegene alifaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ halale kegene mesaęž‰noęž‰ dimidaęž‰lubi.  
\v 4 Moęž‰woęž‰ we, tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale nioęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ imilise dowaki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Mama maliloęž‰ imilise aęž‰noęž‰ ni amioęž‰ tambo dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ tambo enoęž‰le domaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰li hoęž‰idoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ kelegoęž‰ nafale koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ uwa diaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ yasilab aęž‰noęž‰ imiloęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 5 Kalu Alanoęž‰ imilise, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tilidabuwoęž‰ imilise, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ hoęž‰na toęž‰lolan man aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ imilise dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 4.6 \xt 1Kol 12.6\x*Godeyoęž‰ imilig koęž‰loęž‰lab. Kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ Iyayoęž‰ tambo e. Gode e iwalu iliki, nioęž‰ tambo boęž‰foęž‰lab. Eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale tambo i us aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ nanogoęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ e kalukaęž‰isale usamioęž‰ tambo aęž‰lab.   
\p
\v 7 \x - \xo 4.7 \xt Lom 12.3,6\x*Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ boba kelegoęž‰ nimoęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ boęž‰ba kelegoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰woęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ inaęž‰li inaęž‰lile dimiaęž‰i ane koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 4.8 \xt Song 68.18\x*Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰,  
\q1 â€śE iwalu halona haęž‰nakiyoęž‰,  
\q2 ene gis kalu modoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰liaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, dibolowa toęž‰lomaęž‰ni tililiaęž‰gane.  
\q1 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ boba kelegoęž‰ nafayoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale enedoęž‰moęž‰ dimi.â€ť   
\m
\v 9 \x - \xo 4.9 \xt Yoęž‰n 3.13\x*Eyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, â€śE iwalu halona aneâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰? Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, tamin amioęž‰ e henfeloęž‰ amioęž‰ ololo koęž‰le tianekaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰li widaki gab.  
\v 10 Kalu tamin amiloęž‰ ololodoęž‰ tiane aęž‰noęž‰, imilise ekoęž‰ iwalu Hebene halona ane. Eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, Hebene hen amioęž‰loęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wiyoęž‰loęž‰, kelegoęž‰woęž‰ tambo amioęž‰ ilili alitaki goęž‰.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 4.11 \xt 1Kol 12.28\x*Kalu aęž‰maęž‰loęž‰ boba kelegoęž‰ nimoęž‰loęž‰ dimiyoęž‰ we. Kalu noloęž‰ iligaęž‰feloęž‰ kalu domaęž‰ki daęž‰fe alifeloęž‰. Kalu noloęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ dinali samaęž‰ki daęž‰fe alifeloęž‰. Kalu noloęž‰ siaęž‰likiyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ walamaęž‰ki daęž‰fe alifeloęž‰. Kalu noloęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ tili dowaki, Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ walamaęž‰ki daęž‰fe alifeloęž‰.  
\v 12 Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ boba kelegoęž‰ dimi aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale iliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ nanogoęž‰ nafa dimidamaęž‰kiyoęž‰ egoęž‰le ilili alitaki goęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰galikiyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ anayaki, halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ib.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 4.13 \xt Kolo 1.28\x*Nanog nafa aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, nili tilidabu aęž‰namioęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ nililoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene soęž‰wa koęž‰loęž‰ fanda asulumaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ tambo asuloęž‰woęž‰ imiloęž‰le domaęž‰noęž‰. Kalu soęž‰wa koęž‰loęž‰ analiaęž‰gaęž‰ kalu dowan aumboęž‰, nili tilidabuwoęž‰loęž‰ anayaki nafale domaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso e koęž‰loęž‰ egoęž‰le dowoęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, nioęž‰loęž‰ ene man aęž‰noęž‰ imili alitalikiyoęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib.  
\v 14 Nili tilidabuwoęž‰ anayab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, nioęž‰ soęž‰wagalin oęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰domaęž‰ki gab. Nioęž‰ to hoęž‰gi koęž‰liloęž‰ noloęž‰ daęž‰dalikiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ hoęž‰n koęž‰su koęž‰loęž‰ hoęž‰n faęž‰saęž‰ waęž‰l amiloęž‰ fufayaęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰sian aumboęž‰ moęž‰domaęž‰noęž‰. Madaliloęž‰ widan kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ yaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ dikidaki widalikiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ tilidaęž‰dakiyoęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 4.15 \xt Kolo 1.18, 2.19\x*Niliyoęž‰ madali to widab aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰kuduhaęž‰naki, nao no oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki to hendeleyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰melaęž‰niki. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰ nioęž‰ mada analiakiyoęž‰, Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaęž‰melaęž‰niki. Tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale nioęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, nili misaęž‰yoęž‰ Keliso e.  
\v 16 Eya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ heb koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ we tambo kudu alifeloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ amiloęž‰ momayaęž‰loęž‰ kowaęž‰gi alifeloęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ heb koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nanog inidoęž‰leyoęž‰ dimidalikiyoęž‰, nili doęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ analiakiyoęž‰, negeleboęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ib.   
\s1 Nioęž‰ Kelisowa dowaki, man hoęž‰giyoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰niki  
\p
\v 17 \x - \xo 4.17 \xt Lom 1.21, 1Bid 1.14\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niyoęž‰ to nowoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Alanaęž‰ wiya ilikiyoęž‰, niyoęž‰ to we halale soęž‰loęž‰l. Moęž‰tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale ili asuloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ babale dowab koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ man ililoęž‰ dimidab aumboęž‰ dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo.  
\v 18 Ini asuloęž‰woęž‰ kaliaki koęž‰ndoęž‰feleliab koęž‰loęž‰, asuloęž‰ ililoęž‰woęž‰ sololiyaęž‰ goęž‰lufoęž‰liki, iyoęž‰ asugdoęž‰ma dowab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰kudoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 19 Kalukaęž‰isale i amioęž‰ sendelowan manoęž‰ aundoęž‰ma. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ iliyoęž‰ uwoęž‰ dian man aęž‰noęž‰ dimidakiyoęž‰, hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo man mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ dimidaęž‰meleboęž‰losaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asulaęž‰sen.  
\v 20 Koęž‰sega gioęž‰ Keliso amiloęž‰ kudu haęž‰nan man aęž‰noęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, gioęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dimidamaęž‰ki widoęž‰ma.  
\v 21 Yaęž‰suloęž‰ dobaęž‰daęž‰loęž‰ gililoęž‰ dabu aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, gimoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰ asululi aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ to hendele koęž‰loęž‰, Yaęž‰suloęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ mioęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰m.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 4.22 \xt Lom 8.13, Kolo 3.9\x*Gimoęž‰loęž‰ widoęž‰woęž‰ noloęž‰ we. Helebesoęž‰g mogagoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dugulan oęž‰leaumboęž‰, man giloęž‰ amiloęž‰ tamin amiloęž‰ delen aęž‰noęž‰ tambo dilaęž‰bi. Gioęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰kiloęž‰ sendeaęž‰sen man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ dikili alitakiyoęž‰, mada mogagilaęž‰len.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 4.23 \xt Lom 12.2\x*Koęž‰sega Gode eyoęž‰ asuloęž‰ gililoęž‰woęž‰ hoęž‰gi aęž‰nodo alifomaęž‰ki taęž‰taęž‰bi.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 4.24 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 1.26, Kolo 3.10\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ giliyoęž‰ helebesoęž‰g hoęž‰gi koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰gaęž‰lan oęž‰leaumboęž‰, man hoęž‰gi Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ dimidaefaęž‰ daęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰gaęž‰laęž‰bi. Man hoęž‰gi aęž‰noęž‰ man Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰leyoęž‰ oęž‰m koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ dialikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ digaloęž‰le man oęž‰liaęž‰, maliloęž‰le man aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰ib.   
\p
\v 25 \x - \xo 4.25 \xt Sek 8.16, Kolo 3.8-9\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ giliyoęž‰ madaliloęž‰ to saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ka taęž‰taęž‰bi. Nioęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ imilise dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, gegeleboęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰lubi.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 4.26 \xt Song 4.4, Yaęž‰m 1.19-20\x*Gi amioęž‰ kulufaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ dowalikiyoęž‰, giliyoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo. Kulufaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ giloęž‰ amioęž‰ dowalega, ofoęž‰ semoęž‰ tiane amioęž‰, kulufaęž‰yoęž‰ giloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na edaęž‰bi.  
\v 27 Kulufaęž‰yoęž‰ gililoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰edalega, fogoęž‰ Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰moęž‰ dimiab koloęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo.  
\v 28 Gioęž‰ afayoęž‰ diaęž‰lenolalega, waęž‰kabiyoęž‰ afayoęž‰ moęž‰diaki ginin dagiyaęž‰yoęž‰ nanogoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dimidaęž‰lubi. Gililoęž‰ nanog dimidab aęž‰namioęž‰ fowoęž‰ modoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ hedalikiyoęž‰, kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma kalukaęž‰isale nol sab aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰li asuwaęž‰faęž‰ib.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 4.29 \xt Kolo 4.6\x*Giliyoęž‰ kalu noloęž‰ mogailaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰soęž‰bo. Aęž‰laęž‰ba. Giliyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleloęž‰ halale alifaęž‰noęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰lubi. Kalukaęž‰isale to oęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰dab i aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asuwaęž‰faęž‰nikiyoęž‰, giliyoęž‰ towoęž‰ dinafa alobana saęž‰laęž‰lubi.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 4.30 \xt Ais 63.10, Aęž‰fe 1.13-14, 1Tes 5.19\x*Giliyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene Mama maliloęž‰ oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ hidaęž‰maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo. Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ ene soęž‰wale aęž‰laęž‰liki widakiyoęž‰, ene Mamayoęž‰ gimoęž‰ dimi koęž‰loęž‰, ele baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ ge amiloęž‰ difaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ ge hendele gaęž‰li sili alifaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰widaki goęž‰.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 4.31 \xt Kolo 3.8\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ giliyoęž‰ nolboęž‰loęž‰ kele asulaęž‰lowanoęž‰, kulufaęž‰yanoęž‰, gadianoęž‰, towaęž‰loęž‰ keganoęž‰, sadaęž‰danoęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ moęž‰bean man aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ tambo dilaęž‰bi.  
\v 32 \x - \xo 4.32 \xt Madi 6.14, 18.22-35, Kolo 3.12-13\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gegeleboęž‰ nofolakiyoęž‰, haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰lubi. Gode eyoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ gililoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ wiya ilikiloęž‰ gaęž‰lilaęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, giliyoęž‰loęž‰ nolbaęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ gaęž‰lilaęž‰bi.   
\c 5  
\s1 Haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man us aęž‰na dowaęž‰lubi  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 5.1 \xt Madi 5.48\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ niliyoęž‰ man digaloęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰niki. Moęž‰woęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ nioęž‰ mada alan asulaki, nioęž‰ ene soęž‰wale taęž‰foęž‰lab.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 5.2 \xt Kis 29.18, Hibu 10.10\x*Keliso eyoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, ni asuwaęž‰takiyoęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ enedoęž‰koęž‰ walaęž‰. Ene melaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ mundoęž‰ nafale koęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰ba soęž‰mean aumboęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dimi. Oęž‰leaumboęž‰ niliyoęž‰loęž‰ nol oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰maęž‰niki.  
\v 3 Koęž‰sega uwoęž‰ dianoęž‰, moęž‰dimidan aundoęž‰ dimidan man koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ meselan man aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ gi amioęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowabenaęž‰ki, koęž‰naęž‰ dowaęž‰bi. Tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale gioęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰ anidomaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰ililoęž‰.  
\v 4 Giliyoęž‰ waęž‰saęž‰le saęž‰lan to oęž‰liaęž‰, madali to oęž‰liaęž‰, uwoęž‰ diaęž‰nikiloęž‰ mesele saęž‰lan to oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ mada saęž‰laęž‰soęž‰bo. To mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ giliyoęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰ililoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰dimidaki, giliyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lubi.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 5.5 \xt 1Kol 6.9-10, Kolo 3.5\x*Giliyoęž‰ to we hendeleloęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰ asulaęž‰bi. Uwoęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰laboęž‰, moęž‰dimidan aundoęž‰ dimian man koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ dimidaęž‰laboęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ meselaęž‰laboęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale man wengoęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab i aęž‰noęž‰, Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰ man us aęž‰namioęž‰ mada moęž‰tinaęž‰ib. Meselan man aęž‰noęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale madali godemoęž‰loęž‰ gulugululan man oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab.   
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 5.6 \xt Lom 1.18, Kolo 2.4,8\x*Kalu nomaęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ madali to saęž‰lakiyoęž‰ dikidabenaęž‰ki dinafa dowaęž‰bi. Moęž‰woęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale Godeloęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab i aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, man mogagoęž‰ niloęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰i mioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ gadioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale i oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ domaęž‰ib.  
\v 7 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gasa dowaęž‰soęž‰bo.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 5.8 \xt Yoęž‰n 12.36, Aęž‰fe 2.13, Kolo 1.13, 1Bid 2.9\x*Tamin amioęž‰ gioęž‰ sololi usa elen koęž‰sega, oęž‰goęž‰ gioęž‰ Kalu Alan oęž‰liaęž‰ dowabiki, hoęž‰lena aęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ giliyoęž‰ hoęž‰lenaęž‰ soęž‰wayaęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰nan au haęž‰naęž‰lubi.  
\v 9 Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ we. Hoęž‰lenaęž‰ fo hedanoęž‰ we, man nafayoęž‰, man digaloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to hende saęž‰lanoęž‰, fo aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ hedan.  
\v 10 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ giliyoęž‰ manoęž‰ dinafa alobana baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Alandoęž‰ sagalemaęž‰noęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰lekoęž‰ dimidaęž‰lubi.  
\v 11 Sololiyaęž‰ man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ fo nafayoęž‰ moęž‰hedan koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ uwayoęž‰ gasa dowaęž‰soęž‰bo. Aęž‰laęž‰ba. Kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ hendele mogagoęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰asulumaęž‰ki, giliyoęž‰ hoęž‰lena diaęž‰taęž‰bi.  
\v 12 Ililoęž‰ woęž‰noęž‰leloęž‰ dimidan man aęž‰noęž‰ mada mogagoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, niloęž‰ aęž‰saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ sendelowab.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 5.13 \xt Yoęž‰n 3.20-21\x*Koęž‰sega hoęž‰lenaęž‰yoęž‰ man woęž‰noęž‰leloęž‰ delendoęž‰wa doęž‰italikiyoęž‰, kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰na fanda baęž‰baęž‰ib.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 5.14 \xt Ais 26.19, Lom 13.11\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ kelegoęž‰ ililoęž‰ fanda baęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰ tambo hoęž‰len oęž‰ngoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ to wemaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lab,  
\q1 â€śKalu alifoęž‰lab ge sikagama.  
\q2 Ge sowoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ aęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, ge dasima.  
\q1 Aęž‰laęž‰galikiyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene hoęž‰ nafayoęž‰ geloęž‰wa soęž‰soęž‰lemaęž‰ib.â€ť   
\p
\v 15 \x - \xo 5.15 \xt Kolo 4.5\x*Gililoęž‰ man kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa tilidowaki haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Asugdoęž‰ma kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dowaki, asugdoęž‰ di kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaęž‰bi.  
\v 16 Oęž‰goęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dowab koęž‰loęž‰, fogoęž‰ dowalikiyoęž‰ giliyoęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰walaki nanogoęž‰ nafa dimidaęž‰lubi.  
\v 17 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ noęž‰noloęž‰ asugdoęž‰ma kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dowaki, Alanaęž‰loęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dinafa asulaęž‰bi.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 5.18 \xt Luk 21.34\x*Gioęž‰ wain hoęž‰n nakiyoęž‰ dafolaęž‰soęž‰bo. Man aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ mogagilaęž‰maęž‰ib. Koęž‰sega Godeyaęž‰ Mamayoęž‰ gi amioęž‰ ilili alifomaęž‰ki taęž‰taęž‰bi.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 5.19 \xt Kolo 3.16\x*Giliyoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale nol oęž‰liaęž‰ tolakiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ gisaloęž‰ bugoęž‰ amiloęž‰ to sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, gulugululakiloęž‰ gisaloęž‰ moęž‰lan to aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, Mamayaęž‰ gisaloęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ dimiab to aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ giliyoęž‰ Alanaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ wabudaki, asuloęž‰ usamiloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowab aęž‰na aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, gisaloęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰ moęž‰laęž‰bi.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 5.20 \xt Kolo 3.17\x*Hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo amioęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisowaęž‰ wiya ilikiyoęž‰, kelegoęž‰ tambo amioęž‰ Do Godemoęž‰woęž‰ sagalaki, mada oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰lubi.   
\s1 Indiaęž‰ ingaliaęž‰maęž‰ man  
\p
\v 21 \x - \xo 5.21 \xt 1Bid 5.5\x*Giliyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisowoęž‰ mada alan asuloęž‰kaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰widakiyoęž‰, tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale nolbaęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaęž‰bi.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 5.22 \xt Kolo 3.18, 1Bid 3.1\x*Kaęž‰isale giliyoęž‰ Kalu Alanaęž‰ haęž‰g amiloęž‰ dowab oęž‰leau, kalu gililoęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰g amioęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ka dowaęž‰bi.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 5.23 \xt 1Kol 11.3, Aęž‰fe 1.22\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰ Keliso e saęž‰saęž‰ ene misaęž‰ aęž‰lab oęž‰leaumboęž‰, kaluwoęž‰ ene inga aęž‰maęž‰ misaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Saęž‰s kalukaęž‰isale iyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, iloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasili kaluwoęž‰ Yaęž‰su e.  
\v 24 Saęž‰s kalukaęž‰isale koęž‰loęž‰ Kelisowaęž‰ ene haęž‰g amiloęž‰ dowab oęž‰leaumboęž‰, kaęž‰isale gililoęž‰ man dimidan us aęž‰namioęž‰, kalu ginindoęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaęž‰bi.   
\p
\v 25 \x - \xo 5.25 \xt Kolo 3.19, 1Bid 3.7\x*Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰soęž‰ alan asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ ene melaęž‰noęž‰ walaęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, kalu giliyoęž‰ gaęž‰ gayoęž‰ mada alan asulaki haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰bi.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 5.26 \xt Tait 3.5\x*Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, saęž‰s kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ maliloęž‰ dowaki enoęž‰le faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰. Ene to aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, iyoęž‰ hoęž‰naęž‰ toęž‰goęž‰de alitakiyoęž‰, goęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 5.27 \xt 2Kol 11.2, Kolo 1.22\x*Kelisowaęž‰loęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, ene saęž‰s kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ ene siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ gesegoęž‰le dowaki, enoęž‰le domaęž‰ki goęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ ililoęž‰ amiloęž‰ heyoęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰loęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, agogoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ dalagdoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ aundoęž‰ma taęž‰taki, iyoęž‰ maliloęž‰ dowaki, hala dimidoęž‰ nowoęž‰ aundoęž‰ma domaęž‰ki goęž‰.  
\v 28 Aęž‰laęž‰dimidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kalu giliyoęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ asulan oęž‰leaumboęž‰, gaęž‰ gayoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ka alan asulaęž‰bi. Kalu abeyoęž‰ ene ingayoęž‰ mada alan asulab aęž‰noęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ mada alan asuloęž‰kaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰li widakigab.  
\v 29 Moęž‰woęž‰ kalu tambowaęž‰yoęž‰ inin doęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰moęž‰bean. Oęž‰leaumboęž‰ moęž‰aumaęž‰ib. Kalu tambowaęž‰yoęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ inidoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰lakiyoęž‰, maęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ meaki, dinafa tilidowan. Oęž‰leaumboęž‰ Keliso eyoęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰s kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki, mada dinafa tilidowan.  
\v 30 Moęž‰woęž‰ nioęž‰ tambo Kelisowaęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰ heb imilise koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 5.31 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 2.24, Madi 19.5\x*Godeyaęž‰ ene bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰, â€śkaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ iya oęž‰liaęž‰ ano oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, ene inga oęž‰liaęž‰ asuloęž‰ imilise dowaki, aęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ imilise domaęž‰ib.â€ť  
\v 32 \x - \xo 5.32 \xt Kala 19.7\x*To saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰goęž‰ bowoęž‰ alan tiane koęž‰loęž‰, to niloęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰l aęž‰noęž‰ Kelisowaęž‰ ene saęž‰s oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ ualoęž‰ gasa domaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 33 Koęž‰sega to aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ka saęž‰lakigab. Kalu giliyoęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰n asulan oęž‰leaumboęž‰, gaęž‰ gayoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ alan asulaki, haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kaęž‰isale giliyoęž‰loęž‰ ge kaluwoęž‰ alan aęž‰laęž‰asulaki, hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambowoęž‰ manoęž‰ mada sagalemaęž‰noęž‰ dimidaęž‰lubi.   
\c 6  
\s1 Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ soęž‰wayoęž‰, iyayoęž‰, anowoęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ manoęž‰ widoęž‰  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 6.1 \xt Kolo 3.20\x*Soęž‰wale gioęž‰ Kalu Alan oęž‰liaęž‰ kudoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, giliyoęž‰ goęž‰l diaęž‰ goęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ towoęž‰ dinafa kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Man aęž‰noęž‰ mada digaloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 6.2 \xt Lo 5.16\x*Godeyaęž‰ ele saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, â€śGioęž‰ goęž‰loęž‰ goęž‰woęž‰ alanoęž‰ oęž‰m aęž‰laęž‰asulaki, ili haęž‰ga dowaęž‰lubi.â€ť Gode eyoęž‰ ele saęž‰laęž‰i mioęž‰ us aęž‰namioęž‰, ele wemaęž‰ saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, dinali sioęž‰ to oęž‰liaęž‰ sioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, eloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ele wenami koęž‰le dimidoęž‰.  
\v 3 Dinali sioęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ we. â€śGiyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalega, ge sagalaki nafale mesaęž‰ib, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ge henfeloęž‰ wiyoęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ sambo oęž‰mesaęž‰ib.â€ť  
\v 4 \x - \xo 6.4 \xt Song 78.4, Sndn 22.6, Kolo 3.21\x*Iya i giliyoęž‰ kalu soęž‰wa kaęž‰isale soęž‰wa ginidoęž‰woęž‰ gadimaęž‰kiyoęž‰ dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo. Aęž‰laba. Gili soęž‰wa i aęž‰noęž‰ anayab amioęž‰, iliyoęž‰ Alanaęž‰ ene manoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu hamanaęž‰kiyoęž‰, giliyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ digalaki, Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ imoęž‰woęž‰ widaęž‰lubi.   
\s1 Foęž‰l eyoęž‰ madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu oęž‰liaęž‰ i oęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu oęž‰liaęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ manoęž‰ widoęž‰  
\p
\v 5 \x - \xo 6.5 \xt Kolo 3.22-23, Tait 2.9-10, 1Bid 2.18\x*Madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu gioęž‰, Kelisowaęž‰ haęž‰ga iliki, ene to koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰nan aumboęž‰, giliyoęž‰ giloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwaęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaki, ili towoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidaęž‰likiyoęž‰ gioęž‰ tagilaki nanog aęž‰noęž‰ nafale faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ki halale diaęž‰bi.  
\v 6 Giliyoęž‰ nanogoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dimidakiyoęž‰, boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu eyoęž‰ geloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lab hoęž‰len aęž‰namioęž‰, e sagale alifaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, nanogoęž‰ dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo. Koęž‰sega giliyoęž‰ Kelisowaęž‰ ene nanog dian kalu aęž‰laęž‰asulaki, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ nimoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰kiloęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, halale dimidaęž‰lubi.  
\v 7 Giliyoęž‰ nanog aęž‰noęž‰ sagalaęž‰liki diaęž‰lubi. Moęž‰woęž‰ gioęž‰ kaluwaęž‰ nanog diaba. Kalu Alanaęž‰ ene nanog koęž‰loęž‰ diab.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 6.8 \xt 2Kol 5.10, Kolo 3.24-25\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ to we asuluma. Kalu abeyoęž‰ nanog nafaleloęž‰ dimidab aęž‰noęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ alobaęž‰dalikiyoęž‰ waęž‰loęž‰ enedoęž‰ man nafa dimidaęž‰len oęž‰leau diaęž‰ib. Madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kaluwaęž‰le, enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwaęž‰le, iyoęž‰ tambo waęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ka diaęž‰ib.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 6.9 \xt Lom 2.11, Kolo 4.1\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu giliyoęž‰, goęž‰noęž‰n madali nanog dian kalumoęž‰woęž‰ man nafa aęž‰noęž‰koęž‰ dimidaęž‰lubi. Giliyoęž‰ i aęž‰noęž‰ tagi alitaęž‰soęž‰bo. Gioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asuluma. Madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu iloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan hendeleyoęž‰loęž‰, giloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan hendeleyoęž‰loęž‰, tamboloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰laboęž‰ Gode imilise E koęž‰loęž‰ Hebene aęž‰lab. Gode eyoęž‰ wiloęž‰ kalumoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, wiloęž‰ma kalumoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ man imilise aęž‰naka iliki alobaęž‰daęž‰sen.   
\s1 Godeyaęž‰ ene buban kelegoęž‰woęž‰ we  
\p
\v 10 To we saebelakiyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Gioęž‰ Kalu Alan oęž‰liaęž‰ dowaki, halaidoęž‰ enedoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ diaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, e oęž‰liaęž‰ halale kagayaęž‰bi.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 6.11 \xt Lom 13.12, 2Kol 10.4\x*Helebesoęž‰g bubakiloęž‰ saęž‰gaęž‰lan Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ gimoęž‰loęž‰ dimi aęž‰noęž‰ giliyoęž‰ dinafa kaęž‰laęž‰bi. Giliyoęž‰ kaliaęž‰gaęž‰ dimadalialikiyoęž‰, Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ dikilimaęž‰noęž‰ dowalikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ oęž‰li halale kagamaęž‰ib.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 6.12 \xt 1Bid 5.8-9\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ nioęž‰ henfeloęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale we oęž‰liaęž‰ gis diaki bubaęž‰loęž‰ba. Niliyoęž‰ mama koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ halaidoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab oęž‰liaęž‰, sololowoęž‰loęž‰ bisoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ i oęž‰liaęž‰, mama mogagoęž‰ akin amiloęž‰ aęž‰lab oęž‰liaęž‰ gis diaki bubaęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 13 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ giliyoęž‰ babumaęž‰nikiloęž‰ saęž‰gaęž‰lan soęž‰g Godeyaęž‰ enedoęž‰le aęž‰noęž‰ kagedeliaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ halale kagayaęž‰bi. Soęž‰g aęž‰noęž‰ kafoęž‰len amioęž‰, hoęž‰len mogagoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ halale kagafoęž‰liki babumaęž‰ib. Gioęž‰ bubaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰ edakiyoęž‰, halaidoęž‰koęž‰ kagafoęž‰melaęž‰ib.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 6.14 \xt Ais 11.5, 59.17, 1Tes 5.8\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ halaidoęž‰ kagamaęž‰nikiyoęž‰, to hendeleyoęž‰ yafu diaęž‰taęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ man digaloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ foęž‰g galamaęž‰ki saęž‰gaęž‰laęž‰bi.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 6.15 \xt Lom 10.15\x*Budi saęž‰gaęž‰lan oęž‰leaumboęž‰, to nafa haęž‰saloęž‰ domaęž‰noęž‰ mandoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰do alitan aęž‰noęž‰ giliyoęž‰ walamaęž‰niki dimidaliaęž‰bi.  
\v 16 Hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambowoęž‰ gili tilidabuwoęž‰, bioęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ halale taęž‰li dofoęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰galikiyoęž‰, mogagoęž‰leloęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ eyoęž‰ daęž‰ insoęž‰ de waęž‰sowaloęž‰ dowoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ geloęž‰wa sandilalikiyoęž‰, giliyoęž‰ daęž‰ insoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kaęž‰laliki, de aęž‰noęž‰ dalifaęž‰ib.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 6.17 \xt Hibu 4.12\x*Giliyoęž‰ Gode eloęž‰ ni koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ gasili aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ asulumaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, misaęž‰ amiloęž‰ goęž‰foęž‰ ki oęž‰ngoęž‰ saęž‰gaęž‰laęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ Mamayaęž‰ ene helebesi sambo aęž‰noęž‰ taęž‰li dofoęž‰lubi. Helebesi aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ oęž‰m.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 6.18 \xt Luk 18.1, Kolo 4.2, 1Tes 5.17\x*Giliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidakiyoęž‰, Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lubi. Hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambowoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene Mamayaęž‰ halaidoęž‰wa dowaki, Godemoęž‰woęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lubi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gioęž‰ si kagafoęž‰liki Godemoęž‰woęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki dabu baęž‰daęž‰lubi.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 6.19 \xt Kolo 4.3-4, 2Tes 3.1\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ neloęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki, giliyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰woęž‰ we au dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi. Godeyaęž‰ ene to aęž‰noęž‰ ni megoęž‰fa diaęž‰talikiyoęž‰, ne moęž‰tagilaki, ene to nafa woęž‰noęž‰leloęž‰ delen aęž‰noęž‰ kalaba walamaęž‰ki, dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 6.20 \xt 2Kol 5.20, File 1.9\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ niyoęž‰ walamaęž‰ki iligaęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰ ne dibolo amioęž‰ aęž‰na soęž‰l. Niyoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ walamaęž‰noęž‰ dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, ne moęž‰tagilaki halale walamaęž‰kiyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi. \fig Helebesoęž‰g bubakiloęž‰ saęž‰gaęž‰lan aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa kaęž‰laęž‰bi.|alt="Soldiers in armor" src="HK00197B.TIF" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles Â© The British & Foreign Bible Society, 1954, 1967, 1972, 1995." ref="6.11" \fig*   
\p
\v 21 \x - \xo 6.21 \xt Ilig 20.4, Kolo 4.7-8, 2Tim 4.12\x*Tikikus e ene tilidabu aęž‰na ilikiyoęž‰, nili nao nowoęž‰ e, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Kalu Alanaęž‰ ene nanog dian kalu nafale nowoęž‰ e. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ e giloęž‰wa yakiyoęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ ne we au saboęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, nanog niloęž‰ diaęž‰li hoęž‰noęž‰l aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ asulumaęž‰ki saęž‰maęž‰ib.  
\v 22 Hendele niloęž‰ Tikikus e koęž‰loęž‰ giloęž‰ amiloęž‰ iligaęž‰toęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ we. Giliyoęž‰ nioęž‰ we au saboęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asulumaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gioęž‰loęž‰ halale alifomaęž‰ki iligaęž‰toęž‰l.   
\p
\v 23 Niyoęž‰ Do Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ asuwaęž‰fomaęž‰ki dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l. Tilidabu nao nado gioęž‰, haęž‰sa dowan man aęž‰noęž‰ gi amioęž‰ domaęž‰ki dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gili tilidabuwa ilikiyoęž‰, gegeleboęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰maęž‰ki dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 24 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Kelisoloęž‰ mada alan asulan man aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰edakiloęž‰ kudufoęž‰koęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰lab gi oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ ene haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ dowaęž‰biyoęž‰.   